Sorry, I still did not get the point. cargo build --target wasm32-unknown-unknown are not going to work for substrate-based projects. It uses a build.rs, and constructs so many flags to build the wasm file. Then integrate that wasm file into the binary. It looks like executable(client + runtime.wasm) file not binary file + wasm file .
